#project
ShopEZ - Stock Trading Platform (MERN)
Overview: A comprehensive online shopping/stock trading platform built with MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, and Node.js that enables users to explore stocks, execute trades, manage portfolios in real-time, with admin moderation capabilities.

Core Features:
User Authentication - JWT-based secure login and registration with role-based access (USER/ADMIN)
Stock Marketplace - Browse, search, and view detailed stock information with real-time price updates
Trading System - Buy/sell stocks with virtual balance simulation and transaction history
Portfolio Management - Track holdings, profit/loss, and investment performance
Admin Dashboard - Manage stocks, approve trades, monitor user activity
Real-time Visualization - Price charts and market trends using Chart.js/Recharts
Technology Stack:
Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB, JWT, bcryptjs
Frontend: React.js, Bootstrap/Material-UI, Axios, Chart.js
Security: JWT authentication, bcrypt password encryption, CORS, role-based route protection
Development Roadmap:
Environment setup and dependencies
MongoDB schema design (Users, Stocks, Transactions, Portfolio)
Full-stack development with CRUD operations
Security implementation and session management
Responsive UI with data visualization
Testing and validation
Optimization and monitoring
